POLICY SERVER CODE REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------

1. Copy your part2 policy server code to this src directory
2. Your policy server code may not use any non-standard C++ library except the rapidjson located at ../lib/rapidjson
3. Make sure your policy server code can be compiled through a single `make` operation
4. Make sure your policy server code can be cleaned through a single `make clean` operation
5. Make sure your policy server program is named AdvPolicyServer
6. Make sure your policy server program can be started through our run-policy-server.sh script
7. Your policy server program should not expect any command line arguments

Thanks!
